<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Become a Sponsor</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Style for placeholder text */
        input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder {
            font-size: 0.9rem; /* Makes the text smaller */
            color: #999; /* Lighter gray color */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-teal2">
    <div class="form-card">
        <h2>Would You Like to Be a Partner?</h2>
        <p>Would your business, company, organization or church like to become a sponsor?</p><n>
        <p>We would love to learn what you do and hear your ideas!</p><n> 
        <p>Let us know how we might work together.</p>

        <form action="/submit-sponsor-form" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="first_name">First Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="first_name" name="first_name" placeholder="required" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="last_name">Last Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="last_name" name="last_name" placeholder="required" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="required" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="organization_name">Organization Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="organization_name" name="organization_name" placeholder="required" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="ideas">What are your ideas?</label>
                <textarea id="ideas" name="ideas" rows="4" ></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-teal">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
